					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-409760#post-2396732</guid>
				<title>Staff Post: Reversion Notice</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-409760/scp-1011#post-2396732</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 25 Oct 2015 02:45:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Wogglebug</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1341523</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Version 27 of this article has been reverted, as it modified a sentence in such a way as to change the original meaning. The wording: &quot;SCP-1011's anomalous properties manifest when it is seen by human subjects who will engage in productive labor no later than three hours after the sighting&quot; means that anyone who will work within 3 hours will be affected by the object, whereas &quot;SCP-1011's anomalous properties manifest when it is seen by human subjects, who will engage in productive labor no later than three hours after the sighting&quot; means that it will affect human subjects, who are then made to work no later than three hours afterward. It is possible that this is what the author meant, but if that is the case the change should either be made by the author or with their approval.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
